         <SecondaryPreamble>
            <EnactingText>
               <Para>
                  <Text>The Secretary of State, in exercise of the powers conferred on him by section 77(1) and (4) of the Education (Scotland) Act 1980<FootnoteRef Ref="f00001"/> and of all other powers enabling him in that behalf, hereby makes the following Regulations:</Text>
               </Para>
            </EnactingText>
         </SecondaryPreamble>
